    <!--
      PSG composition (Zelis admins): add this atom to the following Persona PSGs:
        - Persona - IE Account Manager
        - Persona - Enterprise Account Manager
        - Persona - ZNA Account Manager
        - Persona - Enterprise Sales Exec
        - Persona - ZNA Sales Exec
      Should NOT be assigned to: read-only users (use View atom), integration users.
      Standalone OK for: Sales Enablement leads, power users owning deal-team mgmt.
      The Add and Dismiss action buttons in the engagement panel and detail modal use
      FLS to gate themselves; assigning this atom is what turns those actions on.
    -->
    <description
  >Action-tier Marketing Influence atom. View atom + Engagement_Dismissal__c CRUD + OpportunityContactRole CRUD with IsPrimary/Role edit. Grants the Add and Dismiss panel actions. Compose into Account Manager and Sales Exec Persona PSGs; see source comment.</description>
